Rodney Allen Rippy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rodney_Allen_Rippy 0 Rodney Allen Rippy (born July 29, 1968) is an American former child actor. He appeared in TV commercials for the fast-food chain Jack in the Box in the early 1970s, as well as in numerous roles in television and movies.
